  <entry>
    <title>Hexo配置主题Concise及新建文章、分类及标签等操作</title>
    <link href="https://hubowen7.github.io/2020/06/20/Hexo%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98Concise%E5%8F%8A%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E3%80%81%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E5%8F%8A%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E7%AD%89%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C/"/>
    <id>https://hubowen7.github.io/2020/06/20/Hexo%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98Concise%E5%8F%8A%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E3%80%81%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E5%8F%8A%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E7%AD%89%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C/</id>
    <published>2020-06-20T02:23:18.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-06-20T03:50:38.550Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Markdown说明"><a href="#Markdown说明" class="headerlink" title="Markdown说明"></a>Markdown说明</h2><p>Markdown是一种轻量级的标记语言，可以使用户使用简单的纯文本格式编写文档，其后缀一般为<code>.md</code>或<code>.markdown</code>，当前有包括Github等许多网站都是用Markdown来撰写帮助文档。<br>Markdown语法比较好的教程有<a href="https://www.runoob.com/markdown/md-tutorial.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Markdown教程</a>  </p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="Concise主题"><a href="#Concise主题" class="headerlink" title="Concise主题"></a>Concise主题</h2><p>关于博客的建站工作已经在此篇博文<a href="https://hubowen7.github.io/2020/06/15/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo+Github%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99/">如何使用Hexo+Github搭建个人博客网站</a>中提到，本篇博文主要讲一下如何配置Concise主题及利用博客撰写新的博文、添加分类及标签等操作。  </p><h3 id="Concise主题介绍"><a href="#Concise主题介绍" class="headerlink" title="Concise主题介绍"></a>Concise主题介绍</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/sanonz/hexo-theme-concise" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Concise</a>是由Github上的一位博主开发的简约主题，可以支持PC、平板和手机等设备。  </p><h3 id="Concise主题配置"><a href="#Concise主题配置" class="headerlink" title="Concise主题配置"></a>Concise主题配置</h3><p>（1）首先在你的博客的文件夹点击鼠标右键，选择Git Bash here，输入以下命令行在<code>.../themes</code>文件夹添加Concise主题：  </p><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>Bash</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone git@github.com:sanonz&#x2F;hexo-theme-concise.git themes&#x2F;concise</span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;  </span><br><span class="line">（2）在&#96;_config.yml&#96;文件中修改以下代码：  </span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;yml</span><br><span class="line">theme: concise</span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;  </span><br><span class="line">（3）在命令行窗口输入以下命令将Hexo默认的编译器切换为[hexo-renderer-less](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;hexojs&#x2F;hexo-renderer-less)：  </span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;Git Bash</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-less --save</span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;  </span><br><span class="line">（4）清除缓存，预览博客并重新部署：  </span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;Git Bash</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">### 在Concise主题中添加分类、标签  </span><br><span class="line">（1）复制&#96;...&#x2F;themes&#x2F;concise&#x2F;_config.example.yml&#96;文件并在该文件夹下粘贴重命名为&#96;...&#x2F;_config.yml&#96;；  </span><br><span class="line">（2）修改&#96;...&#x2F;_config.yml&#96;中一些配置，具体的修改参见[Concise](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;sanonz&#x2F;hexo-theme-concise)；  </span><br><span class="line">（3）在文件夹点击鼠标右键，选择Git Bash here，输入以下命令行添加新的分类：  </span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;Git Bash</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page categories</span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;  </span><br><span class="line">（4）在&#96;...&#x2F;source&#x2F;categories&#96;文件夹下找到新建的&#96;index.md&#96;文件，打开之后默认内容为：  </span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;Markdown</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 文章分类</span><br><span class="line">date: 2020-06-15 11:03:08</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;  </span><br><span class="line">（5）添加&#96;type: &quot;categories&quot;&#96;，修改完毕后内容为（以我的分类Hexo为例）：  </span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;Markdown</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: Hexo</span><br><span class="line">date: 2020-06-15 11:03:08</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;  </span><br><span class="line">（6）在文件夹点击鼠标右键，选择Git Bash here，输入以下命令行添加新的标签：  </span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;Git Bash</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page tags</span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;  </span><br><span class="line">（7）在&#96;...&#x2F;source&#x2F;tags&#96;文件夹下找到新建的&#96;index.md&#96;文件，打开之后默认内容为：  </span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;Markdown</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 标签</span><br><span class="line">date: 2020-06-15 13:47:40</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;  </span><br><span class="line">（8）添加&#96;type: &quot;tags&quot;&#96;和&#96;layout: tags&#96;，修改完毕后内容为（以我的分类Hexo为例）：  </span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;Markdown</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: tags</span><br><span class="line">date: 2020-06-16 10:25:56</span><br><span class="line">layout: tags</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;  </span><br><span class="line">（9）在命令行输入以下命令新建博文：  </span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;Git Bash</span><br><span class="line">hexo new &quot;博文名&quot;</span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;  </span><br><span class="line">（10）为新建的博文添加分类及标签（以我的博文为例）：  </span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;Markdown</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 如何使用Hexo+Github搭建个人博客网站</span><br><span class="line">categories: </span><br><span class="line">- Hexo</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">- Hexo</span><br><span class="line">- Github</span><br><span class="line">- Node.js</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;  </span><br><span class="line">其中分类为&#96;Hexo&#96;，标签有&#96;Hexo&#96;，&#96;Github&#96;和&#96;Node.js&#96;。  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">### 注意事项   </span><br><span class="line">在添加完分类之后，需要在&#96;...&#x2F;_config.yml&#96;文件的&#96;menu:&#96;处对添加的分类路径进行添加（以我的博客为例）：  </span><br><span class="line">&#96;&#96;&#96;Markdown</span><br><span class="line">  首页: &#x2F;</span><br><span class="line">  Hexo: &#x2F;categories&#x2F;Hexo&#x2F;</span><br><span class="line">  标签: &#x2F;tags&#x2F;</span><br><span class="line">  归档: &#x2F;archives&#x2F;</span><br><span class="line">  关于: &#x2F;about&#x2F;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>添加了<code>Hexo</code>这一分类。</p><h2 id="参考文档及网站"><a href="#参考文档及网站" class="headerlink" title="参考文档及网站"></a>参考文档及网站</h2><ul><li><a href="https://github.com/sanonz/hexo-theme-concise" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Concise</a>  </li></ul><ul><li><a href="https://sanonz.github.io/2017/hello-world/#%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AF-Markdown" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo 搭建静态博客与 hexo-theme-concise 主题使用教程</a>  </li></ul>]]></content>
    
